title: Plot Bunny
body:
by Gobi17

“Gukkie is bunny,” the hybrid said, pointing to his own forehead.

“Gukkie?” Mandiville near-melted on the spot. “Is your name Gukkie?”

The bunny nodded vigorously. “Gukkie,” he tapped his forehead, then pointed behind him at the sleeping huddle. “Hose, Yoo, Tae.” Then with an afterthought, he tapped his own forehead again. “Gukkie.”

The human x hybrid war has been raging for months now. That’s all about to change when a baby bunny hybrid is captured by the humans. He’s scared, and adorable and definitely too dumb to be up to anything suspicious.
